# Source: https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/run-application/run-stateless-application-deployment/

1. Create a Deployment based on the YAML file:
`$ kubectl apply -f ~/custom-k8s-scheduler/samples/deployment.yaml`

2. Display information about the Deployment:
`$ kubectl describe deployment nginx-deployment`

3. Get pods and their nodes
`$ kubectl get pods -o wide`

4. Delete deployment
`$ kubectl delete deploymnt nginx-deployment`